text.section:
"Educational purpose" includes:
Nature study;
Farm visitations for purposes of learning about the farming operation;
Practice judging of livestock, dairy cattle, poultry, other animals, agronomy crops, horticultural crops, or other farm products;
Organized visits to farms by school children, 4-H clubs, FFA clubs, and others as part of their educational programs;
Organized visits for purposes of participating in or observing historical reenactments as part of an educational or cultural program; and
Observation of historical, archaeological, or scientific sites.
